INSERT INTO test_project (project_name, project_product, project_group, project_task, project_case_starttime, project_case_endtime, project_implement_starttime, project_implement_endtime, project_examine_starttime, project_examine_endtime, create_by,test_director, create_time, status)
  VALUES (
		{{Input1.text}}, 
		{{Select1.selectedOptionValue}},
		{{Input2.text}},
		{{Select2.selectedOptionValue}},
		{{moment(DatePicker1.selectedDate).format('YYYY-MM-DD')}}, 
		{{moment(DatePicker1Copy.selectedDate).format('YYYY-MM-DD')}}, 
		{{moment(DatePicker2.selectedDate).format('YYYY-MM-DD')}}, 
		{{moment(DatePicker2Copy.selectedDate).format('YYYY-MM-DD')}}, 
		{{moment(DatePicker3.selectedDate).format('YYYY-MM-DD')}}, 
		{{moment(DatePicker3Copy.formattedDate).format('YYYY-MM-DD')}}, 
		{{appsmith.user.name}},
		{{Select3.selectedOptionValue}},
		{{moment().format("YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss")}},
		1);
